cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with language models and word prediction systems. It may also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves the use of Latent Semantic Analysis (LSA) to extract semantic information. Additionally, the paper may fall under the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it explores methods to integrate semantic information with a standard language model. Finally, it may also belong to Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) as some of the methods proposed may involve neural networks.
